WEBVTT

00:05:28.080 --> 00:05:30.856
in preganjala sem komarje
in skočila na tovornjak

00:05:30.880 --> 00:05:31.906
in pomislila:

00:05:31.930 --> 00:05:33.666
"Zato ljudje delajo v laboratoriju."

00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:35.480
(smeh)

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:38.616
Počakala sem eno uro.

00:05:38.616 --> 00:05:40.342
Predvidevala sem, da bodo v tem času

00:05:40.346 --> 00:05:43.056
drevesa posrkala CO2 v fotosintezi,

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:46.216
ga spremenila v sladkorje,
ga poslala dol do korenin,

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:48.936
in morda, sem predvidevala,

00:05:48.960 --> 00:05:51.760
poslala ogljik pod tlemi k sosedom.

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:54.776
In ko je minila ura,

00:05:54.800 --> 00:05:56.376
sem odprla okno

00:05:56.400 --> 00:05:58.000
in preverila, kje je mama grizli.

00:05:58.600 --> 00:06:01.000
Dobro, tamle je in je borovnice.